{
  "text": "In vitro KMT and Flashplate KMT assays. Lysine methylation assays were performed in reaction buffer (50mM Tris-Cl pH8.0, 10% glycerol, 20mM KCl, 5mM MgCl2) supplemented with 3 H-SAM as described [CITATION_1] , using calf thymus histones (Worthington), recombinant histone tails (see above), or biotinylated histone H4 peptides.",
